moduleDescription:
This file is included in generated parsers to provide common utilities
  • When a parser is generated, it will include this file include treestand/parser_runtime

entries.name: math
entries.code: proc math(): InputGrammar {.raises: [], tags: [], forbids: [].}

entries.name: TerminalSymbol
entries.code:
TerminalSymbol = enum
  tsEOF = 0, tsNumber = 1, tsOp = 2, tsLparen = 3, tsRparen = 4, tsToken_4 = 5

entries.name: NonTerminalSymbol
entries.code:
NonTerminalSymbol = enum
  ntProgram = 0, ntExpression = 1, ntBinary_op = 2, ntPrimary = 3, ntParens = 4,
  ntNumber = 5, ntOp = 6, ntLparen = 7, ntRparen = 8

entries.name: terminalSymbolNames
entries.code: terminalSymbolNames = ["EOF", "number", "op", "lparen", "rparen", "token_4"]

entries.name: nonTerminalSymbolNames
entries.code:
nonTerminalSymbolNames = ["program", "expression", "binary_op", "primary",
                          "parens", "number", "op", "lparen", "rparen"]
